OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying dry.
OL,6,FThere will be clear skies at first,
OL,7,Fbut high cloud spreading in from the
OL,8,Fwest later.
OL,9,
OL,10,CSaturday:FIt will remain dry with some
OL,11,Fbright spells on Saturday, but
OL,12,Fsunshine quite hazy with high level
OL,13,Fcloud. Fresh to strong southerly winds.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunday
OL,16,Fwill be another dry and bright day.
OL,17,FMore cloud on Monday, perhaps some
OL,18,Frain later. Dry start Tuesday, windier
OL,19,Fand cloudier with some rain later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
